.TH CYGNUS-VIEW 1.3 "March 2026" "Version 1.3" "Cygnus Image Viewer"
.SH NAME
cygnus-view \- lightweight image viewer for Cygnus WM

.SH SYNOPSIS
.B cygnus-view
[\fIFILE\fR]

.SH DESCRIPTION
.B cygnus-view
is a simple, fast image viewer written for the Cygnus Window Manager. If no file is provided, it launches a file picker (\fBcygnus-open\fR).

.SH KEY BINDINGS
.TP
.B Left Arrow
Previous image in directory.
.TP
.B Right Arrow
Next image in directory.
.TP
.B Up Arrow
Zoom in.
.TP
.B Down Arrow
Zoom out.
.TP
.B q, Escape
Exit the viewer.

